### Send a message
POST {{host}}/chat/{{conversationId}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "message": "Hello from Gimlee Chat!"
}

### Get chat history
GET {{host}}/chat/{{conversationId}}/messages?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get chat history (with cursor pagination)
GET {{host}}/chat/{{conversationId}}/messages?limit=20&beforeId={{messageId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Indicate typing
POST {{host}}/chat/{{conversationId}}/typing
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Subscribe to chat events (SSE)
GET {{host}}/chat/{{conversationId}}/events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: text/event-stream
